snippet.title: Crackernuts - Official Trailer | Ghouls 4 Games
snippet.description: Explore the handmade fairytale world of Crackernuts in this trailer for the upcoming short narrative adventure game based on a Scottish fairytale about a girl with the head of a goat. Crackernuts will be available on PC and Nintendo Switch.
